All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionTrackerPlugin
    Main class that registers events and commands into the server.
    BlockRange2D
    Represents rectangular boundary.
    DynamicMapRenderer
    The "Google Maps" implementation that assists players traversing through the missions.
    DynamicMapRenderer.CustomMap  
    EnhancedStatsTracker
    Enhanced stats tracker that builds off of the StreamlinedStatsTracker to give data useful for a recommendation system.
    GraphGenerator
    Creates graphical representations used by the recommendation best path system from CSV files.
    GraphGenerator.DecisionPoint
    Represents a decision point in the mapping.
    GraphGenerator.EnclosedSpace
    Represents an empty space that is enclosed by doors or walls.
    GraphGenerator.Point
    Integer representation of a point.
    GraphGenerator.PointPath
    Represents a path through the mapping.
    MapOverlayRenderer
    Simple map overlay renderer that will only show the player on the map without rotating or translating the map.
    Mission
    Holds all data related to a particular mission.
    MissionCommandHandler
    Command manager that allows the player to start commands (particularly, start the mission) and other various options.
    MissionEventListener
    Tracks player actions while the mission is active to store into stats.
    MissionGraph
    Class holding the graphical representation of a mission map with room and decision vertices.
    MissionGraph.MissionVertex  
    MissionGraph.MissionVertexType  
    MissionManager
    Handles a mission active/inactive state, as well as the mission logistics overall (including countdown).
    MissionRoom
    Represents a room on a map.
    PlayerAnalyzer
    Handles player-specific actions and recommendations: particularly, the best path recommendations, speed analysis, and edge creation/deletion algorithms are run here.
    PlayerAnalyzer.Direction
    Used to assist with telling the player where to go relative to their current facing direction (ex: go left).
    PreciseVisibleBlocksRaycaster
    Standalone class that will determine blocks currently visible to any given player.
    SelectionWand
    Implementation of SpecialItem class that determines the boundaries of a left/right click to define a room boundary.
    SpecialItem
    Generic SpecialItem class that allows special implementations to be made.
    SpecialItem.ItemEventHooks  
    SpecialItemEventListener
    Event Listener class that will call events for any SpecialItem implementations.
    StatsTracker
    Interface class to represent different types of stat trackers.
    StreamlinedStatsTracker
    Work in progress stats tracker that will output JSON files that will as closely match Malmo parsed files as possible, and that's it.
    Utils
    Holds miscellaneous utility functions used throughout the project.
    WorldManager
    Helper class that will autoload worlds that were not part of the original worlds (typically world, world_nether, world_end).
